Introduction

Lee Jae Jun, or simply Jaejun, is a seasoned artist in the K-pop industry, bringing years of experience to his latest venture as a member of IN A MINUTE, a trio under JWIN Entertainment. Having previously been part of groups like C-CLOWN, TREI, and TAN, as well as the duo JT&MARCUS, Jaejun has showcased his versatility as a vocalist, performer, and songwriter. His participation in survival shows such as MIXNINE and Wild Idol further solidified his reputation as a dedicated and skilled artist. Now, alongside Juntae and Hyunyeop, he is set to debut with IN A MINUTE on March 15, 2025, with their first single album, UNBOXING: WHAT YOU WANTED.

On November 10, 2024, Jaejun announced his departure from MLD Entertainment. Shortly after, on February 19, 2025, he signed an exclusive contract with JWIN Entertainment, joining the trio IN A MINUTE alongside Juntae and Hyunyeop. With his move to JWIN, JT&MARCUS has likely disbanded, as both Jaejun and Juntae have embarked on this new chapter.
